鰆字的基本解释

鰆
chūn
〔鰆鱼〕体长而侧扁，银灰色，有暗色横纹或斑点，鳞细小或无鳞，口大，吻尖。生活于海洋，常成群作远程洄游。性凶猛，捕食小鱼。亦称“马鲛”。

chūn
〔鰆鱼〕The body is long and flat, silver-gray, with dark stripes or spots, small or no scales, a large mouth, and a pointed snout. Living in the ocean, they often migrate in groups for long distances. It is fierce and preys on small fish. Also known as "horse mackerel".
